dataList.appIntro:
The Real Madrid C.F. official keyboard is here! The best keyboard app from the best football club in the world! Get closer to your favorite football team with our smart keyboard and all its unique features. Hala Madrid!
 
Real Madrid keyboard is much more than a simple keyboard. Enjoy Real Madrid styled themes, news, stickers and more. Choose the best themes featuring the most popular soccer players such as Cristiano Ronaldo, Gareth Bale, Sergio Ramos, Karim Benzema, Marcelo and many more! Stay up-to-date with official news and updates from the best football club of the century and get the chance to win an official signed Real Madrid jersey and other merchandises with our giveaways! Plus, new and more exciting features are coming soon!
 
And the best part is… it’s available completely FREE of charge!
 
★Real Madrid Kika Keyboard Key Features★
•Custom Real Madrid styled keyboard
•Various Real Madrid keyboard themes
•Unique Real Madrid stickers featuring Cristiano Ronaldo, Marcelo and more
•Up-to-date Real Madrid news 
•Giveaways - Get the chance to win an official signed Real Madrid jersey and other merchandises
•1600+ Emoji & Emoticons
•Supports 100+ Languages/Dictionaries  
•Word Predictions & Suggestions
•Swipe-to-Type
•Personal Dictionary 
•Smart Autocorrect 
•Customized layouts including one-hand mode, split screen & resize options 
•Full support for Android mobiles and tablets
 
Multilingual Support
Real Madrid Kika Keyboard supports the following languages:
Afrikaans, Albanian, Amharic, Arabic, Aragonese, Armenian, Assamese, Asturian, Azerbaijani, Bashkir, Basque, Belarusian, Bengali, Bodo, Bosnian, Breton, Bulgarian, Burmese, Catalan, Chechen, Chinese (Traditional and Simplified), Chuvash, Croatian, Czech, Danish, Divehi, Dogri, Dutch, English, Esperanto, Estonian, Estonian, Faroese, Filipino, Finnish, French, Galician, Georgian, German, Greek, Gujarati, Hausa, Hebrew, Hindi, Hinglish, Hungarian, Icelandic, Igbo, Indonesian, Irish, Italian, Javanese, Kannada, Kashmiri, Kazakh, Khmer, Kinyarwanda, Konkani, Korean, Kurdish, Kyrgyz, Laotian, Latvian, Lithuanian, Low German, Luxembourgish, Macedonian, Maithili, Malagasy, Malay, Malayalam, Maltese, Manipuri, Marathi, Mongolian, Nepali, Norwegian, Occitan, Oriya, Oromo, Pashto, Persian, Polish, Portuguese, Punjabi, Romanian, Russian, Sakha, Sanskrit, Santali, Scottish Gaelic, Serbian, Sindhi, Sinhalese, Slovak, Slovenian, Spanish, Sundanese, Swahili, Swedish, Tagalog, Tajik, Tamil, Tatar, Telugu, Thai, Tigre, Turkish, Turkmen, Ukrainian, Urdu, Uzbek, Vietnamese, Welsh, Western Frisian, Xhosa, Yoruba, Zulu and even more in the making!
 
Privacy and Security
You may receive a warning when activating saying “This keyboard may collect your personal data.” We take your privacy seriously. This keyboard does not collect your private data including password or credit card information. The warning message when you enable is a standard message in Android for ANY third-party keyboard.
